metadata.name: Class of 2022 #1/296
metadata.description:
Class of 2022 is a token of gratitude for holders of Jeremy Knows' Gen 0 NFT.

Hang this one-of-a-kind ornament in your wallet and watch as it brings a burst of color and whimsy to your collection. The glossy, hand-painted finish features swirling patterns in vibrant shades of fuchsia, teal, and gold, giving it a psychedelic flair. At the center of the ornament is inscribed '2022,' making it a special memento for this graduating class. Whether displayed on its own or paired with other ornaments, this eye-catching piece is sure to be a conversation starter and bring joy to your holiday season.

The art & description of this piece were created partly with AI tools.
